title: |md
  # TCP Fast Recovery State Machine
  RFC 5681 Fast Retransmit/Recovery Flow
| {near: top-center}
# Initial state - Normal operation
Normal: "Normal Operation\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\ncwnd < ssthresh (Slow Start)\nor cwnd в‰Ґ ssthresh (Congestion Avoidance)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nвЂў Process ACKs normally\nвЂў Increase cwnd per phase rules" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#E8F5E9"
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
# Duplicate ACK tracking
DupACK1: "1st Duplicate ACK\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\ndup_ack_count = 1\nвЂў ACK num unchanged\nвЂў Send immediate ACK" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#FFF3E0"
  style.stroke: "#E65100"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
DupACK2: "2nd Duplicate ACK\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\ndup_ack_count = 2\nвЂў ACK num unchanged\nвЂў Send immediate ACK" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#FFE0B2"
  style.stroke: "#E65100"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
# Fast Retransmit trigger
FastRetransmit: "Fast Retransmit Triggered\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n3rd Duplicate ACK received\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nвЂў dup_ack_count = 3\nвЂў TRIGGER FAST RETRANSMIT" {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#FFCDD2"
  style.stroke: "#C62828"
  style.stroke-width: 3
}
# Loss recovery actions
LossRecovery: "Enter Loss Recovery\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nssthresh = max(cwnd/2, 2*MSS)\ncwnd = ssthresh + 3*MSS\nrecover_seq = SND.NXT\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nвЂў Cancel retransmit timer\nвЂў Retransmit segment at SND.UNA" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#E1BEE7"
  style.stroke: "#7B1FA2"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
# Fast recovery state
FastRecovery: "Fast Recovery\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nState: in_recovery = TRUE\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nFor each additional duplicate ACK:\n  вЂў cwnd += MSS (window inflation)\n  вЂў Can send new segment if allowed\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nWhy +3? 3 segments left network (3 dup ACKs)\nWhy inflate? Each dup ACK = segment left network" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#B39DDB"
  style.stroke: "#4A148C"
  style.stroke-width: 3
  style.font-color: "#FFFFFF"
}
# Partial ACK handling
PartialACK: "Partial ACK Received\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nACK advances SND.UNA but\nSEQ_LE(ack_num, recover_seq)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nвЂў Retransmit first unacked segment\nвЂў cwnd -= MSS (deflate)\nвЂў Continue recovery" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#FFCC80"
  style.stroke: "#E65100"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
# Full recovery exit
FullRecovery: "Full ACK Received\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nACK advances past recover_seq\nSEQ_GT(ack_num, recover_seq)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nEXIT RECOVERY:\nвЂў cwnd = ssthresh\nвЂў in_recovery = FALSE\nвЂў Re-arm retransmit timer" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#C8E6C9"
  style.stroke: "#1B5E20"
  style.stroke-width: 3
}
# State transitions
Normal -> DupACK1: "Duplicate ACK\n(ack_num unchanged)" {
  style.stroke: "#E65100"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
DupACK1 -> DupACK2: "Duplicate ACK\n(ack_num unchanged)" {
  style.stroke: "#E65100"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
DupACK2 -> FastRetransmit: "3rd Duplicate ACK\nTRIGGERS FAST RETRANSMIT" {
  style.stroke: "#C62828"
  style.stroke-width: 3
  style.bold: true
}
FastRetransmit -> LossRecovery: "Execute\nrecovery actions" {
  style.stroke: "#7B1FA2"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
LossRecovery -> FastRecovery: "Enter\nfast recovery" {
  style.stroke: "#4A148C"
  style.stroke-width: 3
}
FastRecovery -> FastRecovery: "Additional dup ACK:\ncwnd += MSS\n(inflate window)" {
  style.stroke: "#4A148C"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
FastRecovery -> PartialACK: "Partial ACK:\nSND.UNA advances\nbut not past recover_seq" {
  style.stroke: "#E65100"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
PartialACK -> FastRecovery: "Continue\nin recovery" {
  style.stroke: "#7B1FA2"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
FastRecovery -> FullRecovery: "Full ACK:\nSEQ_GT(ack_num, recover_seq)" {
  style.stroke: "#1B5E20"
  style.stroke-width: 3
  style.bold: true
}
FullRecovery -> Normal: "Resume normal\noperation" {
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.stroke-width: 3
}
# Reset on normal ACK
DupACK1 -> Normal: "New ACK\n(ack_num advances)" {
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
DupACK2 -> Normal: "New ACK\n(ack_num advances)" {
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
# Legend
legend: {
  near: bottom-right
  style.fill: "#FAFAFA"
  style.stroke: "#9E9E9E"
  trigger: "Trigger Condition" {
    shape: diamond
    style.fill: "#FFCDD2"
    style.stroke: "#C62828"
  }
  recovery: "Recovery State" {
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#B39DDB"
    style.stroke: "#4A148C"
  }
  exit: "Exit State" {
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#C8E6C9"
    style.stroke: "#1B5E20"
  }
  note: |md
    **Key Variables:**
    - `cwnd`: Congestion window (MSS units)
    - `ssthresh`: Slow start threshold
    - `recover_seq`: Recovery starting point
    - `dup_ack_count`: Duplicate ACK counter
  |
}
# Algorithm summary
algorithm: |md
  ## Fast Recovery Algorithm (RFC 5681)
  **On 3rd Duplicate ACK:**
  
  ssthresh = max(FlightSize/2, 2*MSS)
  cwnd = ssthresh + 3*MSS
  recover_seq = SND.NXT
  Retransmit segment at SND.UNA
  
  **On each additional duplicate ACK:**
  
  cwnd += MSS  // Inflate window
  // Can send new segment if allowed
  
  **On partial ACK (SND.UNA < ack в‰¤ recover_seq):**
  
  cwnd -= MSS  // Deflate window
  Retransmit first unacked segment
  
  **On full ACK (ack > recover_seq):**
  
  cwnd = ssthresh
  in_recovery = FALSE
  
| {near: bottom-left}